1579void LegacyInlineFlowBox::clearTruncation()
1580{
1581 for (auto* box = firstChild(); box; box = box->nextOnLine())
1582 box->clearTruncation();
1583}
1584
1585LayoutUnit LegacyInlineFlowBox::computeOverAnnotationAdjustment(LayoutUnit allowedPosition) const
1586{
1587 LayoutUnit result;
1588 for (auto* child = firstChild(); child; child = child->nextOnLine()) {
1589 if (child->renderer().isOutOfFlowPositioned())
1590 continue; // Positioned placeholders don't affect calculations.
1591
1592 if (is<LegacyInlineFlowBox>(*child))
1593 result = std::max(result, downcast<LegacyInlineFlowBox>(*child).computeOverAnnotationAdjustment(allowedPosition));
1594
1595 if (child->renderer().isReplaced() && is<RenderRubyRun>(child->renderer()) && child->renderer().style().rubyPosition() == RubyPosition::Before) {
1596 auto& rubyRun = downcast<RenderRubyRun>(child->renderer());
1597 RenderRubyText* rubyText = rubyRun.rubyText();
1598 if (!rubyText)
1599 continue;
1600
1601 if (!rubyRun.style().isFlippedLinesWritingMode()) {
1602 LayoutUnit topOfFirstRubyTextLine = rubyText->logicalTop() + (rubyText->firstRootBox() ? rubyText->firstRootBox()->lineTop() : 0_lu);
1603 if (topOfFirstRubyTextLine >= 0)
1604 continue;
1605 topOfFirstRubyTextLine += child->logicalTop();
1606 result = std::max(result, allowedPosition - topOfFirstRubyTextLine);
1607 } else {
1608 LayoutUnit bottomOfLastRubyTextLine = rubyText->logicalTop() + (rubyText->lastRootBox() ? rubyText->lastRootBox()->lineBottom() : rubyText->logicalHeight());
1609 if (bottomOfLastRubyTextLine <= child->logicalHeight())
1610 continue;
1611 bottomOfLastRubyTextLine += child->logicalTop();
1612 result = std::max(result, bottomOfLastRubyTextLine - allowedPosition);
1613 }
1614 }
1615
1616 if (is<LegacyInlineTextBox>(*child)) {
1617 const RenderStyle& childLineStyle = child->lineStyle();
1618 std::optional<bool> markExistsAndIsAbove = downcast<LegacyInlineTextBox>(*child).emphasisMarkExistsAndIsAbove(childLineStyle);
1619 if (markExistsAndIsAbove && *markExistsAndIsAbove) {
1620 if (!childLineStyle.isFlippedLinesWritingMode()) {
1621 int topOfEmphasisMark = child->logicalTop() - childLineStyle.fontCascade().emphasisMarkHeight(childLineStyle.textEmphasisMarkString());
1622 result = std::max(result, allowedPosition - topOfEmphasisMark);
1623 } else {
1624 int bottomOfEmphasisMark = child->logicalBottom() + childLineStyle.fontCascade().emphasisMarkHeight(childLineStyle.textEmphasisMarkString());
1625 result = std::max(result, bottomOfEmphasisMark - allowedPosition);
1626 }
1627 }
1628 }
1629 }
1630 return result;
1631}
1632
1633LayoutUnit LegacyInlineFlowBox::computeUnderAnnotationAdjustment(LayoutUnit allowedPosition) const
1634{
1635 LayoutUnit result;
1636 for (auto* child = firstChild(); child; child = child->nextOnLine()) {
1637 if (child->renderer().isOutOfFlowPositioned())
1638 continue; // Positioned placeholders don't affect calculations.
1639
1640 if (is<LegacyInlineFlowBox>(*child))
1641 result = std::max(result, downcast<LegacyInlineFlowBox>(*child).computeUnderAnnotationAdjustment(allowedPosition));
1642
1643 if (child->renderer().isReplaced() && is<RenderRubyRun>(child->renderer()) && child->renderer().style().rubyPosition() == RubyPosition::After) {
1644 auto& rubyRun = downcast<RenderRubyRun>(child->renderer());
1645 RenderRubyText* rubyText = rubyRun.rubyText();
1646 if (!rubyText)
1647 continue;
1648
1649 if (rubyRun.style().isFlippedLinesWritingMode()) {
1650 LayoutUnit topOfFirstRubyTextLine = rubyText->logicalTop() + (rubyText->firstRootBox() ? rubyText->firstRootBox()->lineTop() : 0_lu);
1651 if (topOfFirstRubyTextLine >= 0)
1652 continue;
1653 topOfFirstRubyTextLine += child->logicalTop();
1654 result = std::max(result, allowedPosition - topOfFirstRubyTextLine);
1655 } else {
1656 LayoutUnit bottomOfLastRubyTextLine = rubyText->logicalTop() + (rubyText->lastRootBox() ? rubyText->lastRootBox()->lineBottom() : rubyText->logicalHeight());
1657 if (bottomOfLastRubyTextLine <= child->logicalHeight())
1658 continue;
1659 bottomOfLastRubyTextLine += child->logicalTop();
1660 result = std::max(result, bottomOfLastRubyTextLine - allowedPosition);
1661 }
1662 }
1663
1664 if (is<LegacyInlineTextBox>(*child)) {
1665 const RenderStyle& childLineStyle = child->lineStyle();
1666 std::optional<bool> markExistsAndIsAbove = downcast<LegacyInlineTextBox>(*child).emphasisMarkExistsAndIsAbove(childLineStyle);
1667 if (markExistsAndIsAbove && !*markExistsAndIsAbove) {
1668 if (!childLineStyle.isFlippedLinesWritingMode()) {
1669 LayoutUnit bottomOfEmphasisMark { child->logicalBottom() + childLineStyle.fontCascade().emphasisMarkHeight(childLineStyle.textEmphasisMarkString()) };
1670 result = std::max(result, bottomOfEmphasisMark - allowedPosition);
1671 } else {
1672 LayoutUnit topOfEmphasisMark { child->logicalTop() - childLineStyle.fontCascade().emphasisMarkHeight(childLineStyle.textEmphasisMarkString()) };
1673 result = std::max(result, allowedPosition - topOfEmphasisMark);
1674 }
1675 }
1676 }
1677 }
1678 return result;
1679}
1680
1681void LegacyInlineFlowBox::collectLeafBoxesInLogicalOrder(Vector<LegacyInlineBox*>& leafBoxesInLogicalOrder, CustomInlineBoxRangeReverse customReverseImplementation, void* userData) const
1682{
1683 LegacyInlineBox* leaf = firstLeafDescendant();
1684
1685 // FIXME: The reordering code is a copy of parts from BidiResolver::createBidiRunsForLine, operating directly on InlineBoxes, instead of BidiRuns.
1686 // Investigate on how this code could possibly be shared.
1687 unsigned char minLevel = 128;
1688 unsigned char maxLevel = 0;
1689
1690 // First find highest and lowest levels, and initialize leafBoxesInLogicalOrder with the leaf boxes in visual order.
1691 for (; leaf; leaf = leaf->nextLeafOnLine()) {
1692 minLevel = std::min(minLevel, leaf->bidiLevel());
1693 maxLevel = std::max(maxLevel, leaf->bidiLevel());
1694 leafBoxesInLogicalOrder.append(leaf);
1695 }
1696
1697 if (renderer().style().rtlOrdering() == Order::Visual)
1698 return;
1699
1700 // Reverse of reordering of the line (L2 according to Bidi spec):
1701 // L2. From the highest level found in the text to the lowest odd level on each line,
1702 // reverse any contiguous sequence of characters that are at that level or higher.
1703
1704 // Reversing the reordering of the line is only done up to the lowest odd level.
1705 if (!(minLevel % 2))
1706 ++minLevel;
1707
1708 Vector<LegacyInlineBox*>::iterator end = leafBoxesInLogicalOrder.end();
1709 while (minLevel <= maxLevel) {
1710 Vector<LegacyInlineBox*>::iterator it = leafBoxesInLogicalOrder.begin();
1711 while (it != end) {
1712 while (it != end) {
1713 if ((*it)->bidiLevel() >= minLevel)
1714 break;
1715 ++it;
1716 }
1717 Vector<LegacyInlineBox*>::iterator first = it;
1718 while (it != end) {
1719 if ((*it)->bidiLevel() < minLevel)
1720 break;
1721 ++it;
1722 }
1723 Vector<LegacyInlineBox*>::iterator last = it;
1724 if (customReverseImplementation) {
1725 ASSERT(userData);
1726 (*customReverseImplementation)(userData, first, last);
1727 } else
1728 std::reverse(first, last);
1729 }
1730 ++minLevel;
1731 }
1732}
1733
1734void LegacyInlineFlowBox::computeReplacedAndTextLineTopAndBottom(LayoutUnit& lineTop, LayoutUnit& lineBottom) const
1735{
1736 for (const auto* box = firstChild(); box; box = box->nextOnLine()) {
1737 if (is<LegacyInlineFlowBox>(*box))
1738 downcast<LegacyInlineFlowBox>(*box).computeReplacedAndTextLineTopAndBottom(lineTop, lineBottom);
1739 else {
1740 if (box->logicalTop() < lineTop)
1741 lineTop = box->logicalTop();
1742 if (box->logicalBottom() > lineBottom)
1743 lineBottom = box->logicalBottom();
1744 }
1745 }
1746}
